Package net.delugan.teachly.exercisegenerator

Class ExerciseGenerator

java.lang.Object
net.delugan.teachly.utils.DateTracked
net.delugan.teachly.utils.AuthorAndDateTracked
net.delugan.teachly.exercisegenerator.ExerciseGenerator
@Entity public class ExerciseGenerator extends AuthorAndDateTracked
Entity class representing an exercise generator in the system. Exercise generators are templates that can create multiple similar exercises.
